38
00:04:34,040 --> 00:04:37,670
Thanks to this treaty, the restoration of diplomatic relations between our Kingdom...

39
00:04:37,690 --> 00:04:41,150
...and the Empire is finally starting to look like a real possibility.

40
00:04:41,290 --> 00:04:45,090
So, this marathon of a war is finally gonna end, huh?

41
00:04:47,010 --> 00:04:51,600
Civilian interaction will become commonplace, and citizens of both nations will take each other by the hand.

42
00:04:52,240 --> 00:04:56,330
We'll see the birth of a nation that's prosperous in the truest sense of the word.

43
00:04:57,210 --> 00:05:00,610
Not a nation where only a select few prosper.

44
00:05:00,810 --> 00:05:01,800
You know?

45
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:06,750
There's no telling when the times will change.

46
00:05:09,090 --> 00:05:11,560
Even so, I want to believe in them.

47
00:05:11,920 --> 00:05:15,720
I want to believe in the people who chose THIS solution at THIS time.

48
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:18,220
And that includes you.

49
00:05:18,460 --> 00:05:21,860
Me, I just go with the flow with those times.

50
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:25,940
Well, let's leave the question of the truth of that statement for another time, okay?

51
00:05:26,470 --> 00:05:29,870
